136
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:19,496
Commander, look at this. The Spark has published the photo.

137
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:29,340
<i>[Miss Mu is getting married, but has an affair with Commander Tan]</i>

138
00:11:30,890 --> 00:11:33,776
