250
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:55,614
Deal.

251
00:20:02,900 --> 00:20:04,918
What did Tan Xuanlin say?

252
00:20:05,877 --> 00:20:07,400
Our family's reputation

253
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:10,530
