356
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:10,710
But this time,

357
00:28:10,710 --> 00:28:12,864
I'm not going to let you have her.

358
00:28:14,860 --> 00:28:17,850
It's not wrong for me to pursue the happiness I want.

359
00:28:17,850 --> 00:28:21,300
