398
00:32:23,510 --> 00:32:26,101
I always took Guangyao as my elder brother.

399
00:32:26,101 --> 00:32:28,518
The person I like is Xuanlin.

400
00:32:32,286 --> 00:32:34,050
Father.

401
00:32:36,353 --> 00:32:37,520
Wanqing,

402
00:32:37,520 --> 00:32:40,970
